Class AgentRegistry

java.lang.Object
AI.registry.AgentRegistry
public final class AgentRegistry extends Object
Central registry for managing available AI agent types and their factories.

This class handles the registration of different AI implementations (e.g., MCTS, Random, AlphaZero) and provides a unified interface for creating factories, configurations, and agent instances based on string identifiers.

      public AIAdaptationConfig createConfig(String type, Player player, int iterations)
